#28000
Gathering Circle~
The trees of this area seem to have burned away, stumps and all, leaving
the ground nothing more than earth and ash.  Carved into the ground is an
elaborate series of channels and grooves, generally organized around a
hexagonal pattern within a large circle about thirty feet across.  The
surrounding forest is silent, as if no creature dared to approach.  Around
the edge of the circle are six jagged, twisted obsidian shards, reaching
towards the heavens.  They stand at the six points of the hexagon, and
vibrate ever so slightly.  Twenty feet tall, and jet black, they give you an
ominous feeling of trepidation.  At the center of the room is a great slab
of obsidian, carved with ancient runes of channeling and power.  The runes
that cover the altar appear to be coated with a dried, dark substance.  A
fresh trail provides escape to the south.
~
