for them to behold.  Not darkness, not extremely bright light, but utter
nothingness.  When your eyes snap shut a whole world explodes within the
sonfines of your mind filling it to the bursting point with countless 
millions of shadows all screaming demands and wishes.  There cries fill
your ears and were there anyone standing with you they could hear the
screams.  Not from your mouth, but through your ears.  So loud and angry
are they that your eardrums reverberate there screaching voices out 
into the nothing.  The eyes of the shadows burn wholes in the very fabric
of your mind, scarring it for all eternity.  You will not soon forget this
trip into the Shadow's realm.
